Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will be a day\Nworth commemorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear on my life, they'll\Nnever set foot in my village!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Run straight north!\NRun straight north!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Those mongrels\Nare in big trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,if they so much as\Nlook at my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] How am I supposed\Nto get past this stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI will never...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...let you step foot\Nin that village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did, was lie\Nlike I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Today will be like\Nevery other day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because you and your cronies\Nwill never set foot in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NThey're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't appreciate\Ntardiness. Not one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They know full well\Nwhat happens to those
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,who are foolish enough\Nto upset my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"The Terrifying Duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Meowban Brothers vs. Zoro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great. You guys\Nare really that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NMh-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you have been slower?\NWhat took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] You're the\None who pushed me down
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that oil slick so\Nyou could get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an accident.\NI slipped, you fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,At least one of us\Nmade it outta there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better than both of us\Nbeing stuck at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It shoulda just been you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Run straight north!" he says.\NThat's just great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, how am I\Nsupposed to know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,which way north even\Nis out here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. You're the one who\Nran away so sure of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,ready to take on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just got so excited,\NI started running, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] The sun rises\Nhigh in the sky now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And that means, Captain\NKuro grows very impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Men, don't just lie there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell me you're\Ngoing to let them win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just a couple of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NThe fact, is we don't have time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to lollygag around\Nhere any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If our enemy is strong, then we\Nmust become stronger than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, stare deeply\Ninto this ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I will count "one, two,\NJango" and after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you will all begin\Nto grow stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds will heal and\Nyou will grow stronger still.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is he doing?\NIt looks weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to convince them\Nthey're stronger than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NStronger. Stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NOne... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES shouting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] That one guy\Ncompletely destroyed the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's what I call power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought hypnotizing\Npeople was a buncha crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine what the\Nwhole crew can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NNow go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And strike down all\Nwho stand in your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys, you\Nmight wanna move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy. You and I will\Ntake it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES snarling]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY growling]\N--[ZORO] Uhh... Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you let\Nthat freak hypnotize you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. He really is\Na simple-minded idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NDamn you, Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You made one hell\Nof a miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These are not your\Naverage village idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhere's he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Tear it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B] Ah! He's gonna\Ndestroy our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B] He's gonna crush\Nus with it! Everybody run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE C]\NCaptain, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] I suppose watching\Nhim isn't helping anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, Jango,\Nyou will fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NOne... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO, NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:09:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] What? You saw\NKlahadore heading to the shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION] Yeah, and he had this\Nweird, scary look on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NWhat about Kaya? Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NWe'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Usopp Pirates are off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Carrot, would you wake up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. It's way\Ntoo early for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for laziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Horrible things could be\Nhappening right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION] I still think the\Npirates are gonna attack soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know our Captain\Nsaid that was a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think he was\Nthe one that was lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're probably right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was weird.\NHe seemed off yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Captain wasn't\Nhis usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain used to always\Ncome through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless. The thing's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rotten woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you try to make a fool\Nof the great Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Insulting me for having\Nthe blood of a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you don't have\Nto do this, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NKlahadore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NKlahadore, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Klahadore?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NMerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!\NWhat happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, wake up! Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness. You're\Nstill alive. I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] You have to tell me\Nwho did this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore. That's who.\NHe attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a... He's a pirate.\NHe's never been anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NBut... how could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] He got close to you just\Nso he could steal your fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all he's ever wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NIt can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] Then... what Usopp spoke\Nabout yesterday was the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. And that's\Nwhat is most tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When he learned the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,he tried his hardest\Nto get us to hear him out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but we were all\Ntoo shallow-minded,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,too confident in the closed off\Nworld we've lived in for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to listen to a single word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Run, Kaya!\NThey're gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise, this'll all\Nmake sense tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] In our blind protection\Nof the villain in our midst,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we drove away the one brave\Nlad whose desperate resolve
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,he enacted for\Nthe sake and safety
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of every person of this village,\Nincluding you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NSomeone! Anyone! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry needs help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NNo, miss. It's of no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire staff is on leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has been here\Nsince yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I just-- I'll find--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] You cannot let yourself\Nget flustered, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We know the attack has yet\Nto begin, so be calm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and think clearly about\Nwhat it is you have to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] Because if\NKlahadore is the thief
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,we understand him to be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and his goal is your fortune\Nand your mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,then by all means,\Nlet him have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,None of this is worth\Nsacrificing your life over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cruel truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but you are the only one who\Ncan stop Klahadore now, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... this is not... your\Nburden but still I must ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.\NAnd I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a situation\NI can run away from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what consequences I face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will find Klahadore\Nand I will finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS grunting, groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to hold on\Ntighter, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NBut the poles are slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And my hands are sweaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? We still\Ngotta get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NAren't you worried about Kaya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Someone's coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL yelp]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NIt's Kaya. She's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like something's\Ngot her really bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, walking around outside\Nby herself doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's goin' on.\NSomething really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like those guys are\Nprobably down for the count,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,don't ya think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, but Luffy's still trapped\Nunderneath that cat. Just look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, he's fine. You should\Nreally worry about your
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,own injuries by the looks of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NDamn that little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now our whole\Nplan's shot to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna\Ndo with this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro sees this\Nand he'll kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM]\NButchie! Come check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some bad\Nstuff going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE]\NWhat the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot we still have\Nour trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come forth, Meowban Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain?\NDid you call for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM]\NSiam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And Butchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH] Together we\Nare the Meowban Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NUhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Butchie. Siam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We absolutely must\Nget up this hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but as you can plainly\Nsee our path is blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would be so kind\Nas to remove this obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! We couldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks too strong.\NRight, Butchie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, he's strong.\NWay stronger than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelps] Besides we just guard\Nthe ship, not fight people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really not the guys\Nyou want to send into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they're a couple of pansies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they're not\Nthe trump card after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Siam, just do it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams] What?! Please, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go.\NJust stop yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy's crying like a baby.\NWhat are they doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NOf all people, why force
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--[NAMI] that guy into a fight?\N--I'm gonna tear you up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with these claws,\Nyou just wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a vicious killing machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm coming for you,\Nyou bad people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You come any closer and\NI'll cut you in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not joking! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NBastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM]\NToo bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you fell\Nfor my little ruse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you blocked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering what a\Nbrilliant performance I gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let the tiny\Nbit of skill you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,cause you to underestimate\NSiam of the Meowban Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you missing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I would know\Nanything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat Burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NGive me my swords back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you already have a sword,\Nhow greedy can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye, swords.\NGoodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I feel lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] You should take care\Nwith other people's things!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM]\NYou really have to be faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm agile as a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Butchie, you're up! Get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Siam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE]\N'Tastrophe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, Butchie.\NHe got away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's right there!\NNow hold him tight this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, he's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than I thought he'd be,\Neven without all his blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] This is getting\Nworse by the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If Tubby there\Nwoulda landed on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'da been pounded into the dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get him\Nfor sure this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One-Sword Technique's not my\Nforte fellas, but what the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Butchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Siam! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE, SIAM]\NPussy Willow March!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE, SIAM yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good. They got\Nhim on the defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that Zoro\Ncan gain any ground
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,if he's too busy blocking their\Nattacks. I'm gonna help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to shoot\Nat the bad guys, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NBut I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... It was like he moved\Nin front of my shot on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You dumbass. Don't help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NIt's just a thought, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the two of us\Nwho just got saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had actually hit\None of those guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,they would've come\Nafter us instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And we wouldn't have a chance\Nof holding up against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time he\Nwas worried about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NIf I just had one more sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I could take these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get the swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can get them back to Zoro,\Nthere'll be no way he can lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get the swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can barely even\Nstand up on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--[thud]\N--[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWhat do you need swords for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM, BUTCHIE scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm sorry. I can...\Nexplain all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NThe night has long since passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So why is it that you seem
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to have made no\Nprogress on the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain... Kuro... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll-He'll kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they have a falling out?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] He's handling those\Ntwo like they were nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.73,0:24:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI can't find Kuro anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, ZORO]\NKaya, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.90,0:24:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.95,0:24:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.86,0:24:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NStill asleep! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.99,0:24:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO, NAMI]\NWake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.37,0:24:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI-I'll protect the meat shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.91,0:24:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.66,0:24:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Luffy Back in Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.16,0:24:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya's\NDesperate Resistance!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.58,0:24:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

